          "date": "2013-10-11 15:39:29.000000000",
          "tz": -300
        },
        "subject": "LU-4002 hsm: add hsm_restore_item",
        "message": "LU-4002 hsm: add hsm_restore_item\n\nDivide the action field of hsm_action_item into a enum part and a\nflags part. Do this so that the CDT can send the attributes needed for\nrestore to the copytool. The goal is to revert\nhttp://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/7792/ without allowing the deadlock\ndescribed in LU-4002.\n\n*** Not intended to land as is. For external use only. ***\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ibab6847442a23a54a5170f13d2ef72570cefb991\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
